		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Sure, fsc (color subcarrier) is f/6. But the PPU dot clock is f/4, and the CPU clock is f/12, and you can't skip these dividers without making new CPU and PPU ICs.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


